&thorn;is is &thorn;e tenour of &thorn;e lettre &thorn;at he sent ti&llbar;
hym.  <Q TYPE="letter"><TEXT>
<BODY>
<P>'Darius, kyng of kynges, and lor&dtail; of a&llbar; erthely lordes
