&thorn;a&mtail; how &thorn;at Alexander had&dtail; priue&dtail; hym of
his lordechipe. And &thorn;a&ntail; &thorn;e Atheneanes ware wonder
[wrathe] towardes Alexander, and made grete boste & manace, &thorn;at
&thorn;ay schol&dtail; ryse agaynes hym, bot if he restorede
